---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import RelatedServices from '../../../components/RelatedServices.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Frequently Asked Questions | OnlineTranslation.ae"
  description="Common questions about legal translation in Dubai. MOJ certification, timelines, pricing, and the translation process explained."
>
  <section class="hero-section bg-dark" data-theme="dark">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">HOME</a>
        <span class="separator">&gt;</span>
        <a href="/resources/">RESOURCES</a>
        <span class="separator">&gt;</span>
        <span class="current">FAQ</span>
      </nav>
      
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Common Questions Answered</p>
      <p class="hero-intro">Here are answers to the questions we receive most often. If you cannot find what you are looking for, send us a message and we will be happy to help.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container content-container">
      <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>About Our Services</h2>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What does MOJ certified mean?</h3>
          <p>MOJ (Ministry of Justice) certification means the translation is completed and stamped by a translator licensed by the UAE Ministry of Justice. This certification is required for documents to be accepted by UAE courts, government departments, and many private institutions.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How quickly can you translate my document?</h3>
          <p>Standard turnaround for most single-page documents is same-day. Complex or lengthy documents typically take 2-3 working days. Express service is available for urgent requirements at an additional fee. Send us your document and we will provide an accurate timeline.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What languages do you translate?</h3>
          <p>We specialize in Arabic-English and English-Arabic translation. For other language pairs, we work with a network of certified translators. Contact us to discuss your specific language requirements.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do you provide attestation services?</h3>
          <p>Yes, we can arrange MOFA (Ministry of Foreign Affairs) attestation, embassy legalization, and notarization. We guide you through the full process and handle the logistics.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>Process and Delivery</h2>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How do I send my documents?</h3>
          <p>The quickest way is via WhatsApp. Simply take a clear photo or scan of your document and send it to us. You can also email documents as PDF attachments. For original documents requiring collection, we can arrange courier pickup.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Will I receive a physical copy?</h3>
          <p>Yes, you will receive both a digital copy (PDF) and the original certified hard copy with the MOJ stamp. We deliver across Dubai on the same day and to other Emirates on the following day.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can I collect from your office?</h3>
          <p>Yes, you can collect from our office in Dubai. Please arrange a collection time with us in advance. We will have your documents ready and sealed for pickup.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>Pricing and Payment</h2>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How much does translation cost?</h3>
          <p>Pricing depends on the document type, length, and complexity. Most standard certificates (birth, marriage, degrees) are priced per page. Send us your document for an accurate quote. We do not have hidden fees.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>When do I pay?</h3>
          <p>Payment is required in advance for standard orders. We accept bank transfer, credit/debit cards, and cash on delivery within Dubai. Corporate clients can arrange account terms.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Is there a discount for multiple documents?</h3>
          <p>Yes, we offer volume discounts for multiple documents translated together. Discuss your requirements with us and we will provide a package quote.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>Quality and Accuracy</h2>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What if there is an error in the translation?</h3>
          <p>If you identify an error in our translation, notify us within 7 days of delivery. We will review and correct genuine translation errors at no additional charge. Our quality review process minimizes errors, but we stand behind our work.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Will my translated document be accepted?</h3>
          <p>Our MOJ-certified translations are accepted by UAE courts, government departments, immigration authorities, and most international institutions. If you have specific requirements for a particular authority, let us know and we will ensure compliance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <RelatedServices
        pageKey="faq"
        title="Quick Links"
        showFamily={true}
        showCrossSilo={true}
        maxItems={6}
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container cta-section">
      <h2>Still Have Questions?</h2>
      <p>If you could not find the answer you were looking for, send us a message. We are here to help.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/971508620217" class="btn btn-primary">
        <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> Ask Your Question
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero-section { padding: 8rem 0 4rem; background: var(--primary-color); }
  .breadcrumb { font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .breadcrumb a { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); text-decoration: none; }
  .breadcrumb a:hover { color: #ffffff; }
  .breadcrumb .separator { margin: 0 0.5rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); }
  .breadcrumb .current { color: #ffffff; }
  h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #ffffff; }
  .hero-subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--accent-color); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .hero-intro { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 700px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); }
  .content-container { max-width: 800px; }
  .faq-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .faq-section h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color); }
  .faq-item { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 0.75rem; }
  .faq-item h3 { margin: 0 0 1rem; font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--primary-color); }
  .faq-item p { margin: 0; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-dark); }
  .cta-section { text-align: center; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .cta-section h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cta-section p { margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--accent-color); color: #ffffff; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #e0144c; transform: translateY(-2px); }
</style>
